SQL_STMT_U.val: select s1.tri_class , tr.tr_transnummer , tr.tr_transdatum , tr.tr_indicatie , tr.tr_herkomst_code_tr , tr.tr_mutatiecode , tr.tr_mut_gemaakt , tr.tr_boekdatum , tr.tr_valdatum , tr.tr_aantal , tr.tr_prijs_tr_mntsrt , tr.tr_trans_munts trans_currency , tr.tr_trans_munts_krs trans_quote , tr.tr_trans_munts_fac trans_factor , tr.tr_trans_munts_rcp trans_reciprocal , decode(s1.tri_class,'R1',tr_rel1_rap_munts,tr_rel2_rap_munts) report_currency , decode(s1.tri_class,'R1',tr_rel1_rap_krs, tr_rel2_rap_krs) report_quote , decode(s1.tri_class,'R1',tr_rel1_rap_fac,tr_rel2_rap_fac) report_factor , decode(s1.tri_class,'R1',tr_rel1_rap_rcp, tr_rel2_rap_rcp) report_reciprocal , decode(s1.tri_class,'R1',tr_rel1_rek2_munts,tr_rel2_rek2_munts) account_currency , decode(s1.tri_class,'R1',tr_rel1_munts_krs, tr_rel2_munts_krs) account_quote , decode(s1.tri_class,'R1',tr_rel1_munts_fac,tr_rel2_munts_fac) account_factor , decode(s1.tri_class,'R1',tr_rel1_munts_rcp, tr_rel2_munts_rcp) account_reciprocal , tr.tr_notabedrag , tr_effective_amount , tr.tr_rente , tr.tr_volgnummer , tr.tr_ref_symbool , tr_dealingtijd , b.be_volgnummer , b.be_oms_1 , b.be_aantal_cijfers_display , b.be_prijs_factor , b.be_bi_nummer , tri2.trai_tr_re_id , tri3.trai_tr_re_id cashAccount from ( select tri.trai_tr_volgnummer , decode(tri.trai_tr_account_code,1,'R1',2,'R1',3,'R2',4,'R2',7,'RV','RO') as tri_class from tap_tr_rel_account_info tri inner join rekeningen r on r.re_id = tri.trai_tr_re_id inner join rekeningen_per_product rpp on rpp.rpp_relatienummer= r.re_nummer and rpp.rpp_rekeningsoort = r.re_soort and rpp.rpp_rekening_nummer = r.re_rekening and rpp.rpp_valuta = r.re_muntsoort inner join producten_per_relatie ppr on ppr.ppr_relatienummer = rpp.rpp_relatienummer and ppr.ppr_productnummer = rpp.rpp_productnummer and ppr.ppr_volgnr_per_product = rpp.rpp_volgnr_per_product and ppr.ppr_relatienummer = ~1 and ppr.ppr_productnummer = ~2 and ppr.ppr_volgnr_per_product = ~3 inner join transactions t on t.tr_volgnummer = tri.trai_tr_volgnummer and ((t.tr_transdatum between ~4 and ~5 and t.tr_mut_gemaakt = 'J') or (t.tr_boekdatum between ~4 and ~5 and t.tr_mut_gemaakt = 's' and t.tr_transdatum < ~4 )) group by tri.trai_tr_volgnummer, decode(tri.trai_tr_account_code,1,'R1',2,'R1',3,'R2',4,'R2',7,'RV','RO') ) s1 inner join transactions tr on tr.tr_volgnummer = s1.trai_tr_volgnummer and tr.tr_mut_gemaakt not in ('N','S') and tr.tr_indicatie not in ('TOEK','LOSB', 'YTD') inner join beleggingsinstrument b on b.be_symbool = tr.tr_symbool and b.be_optietype = tr.tr_optietype and b.be_expiratiedatum = tr.tr_expiratiedatum and b.be_exerciseprijs = tr.tr_exerciseprijs left outer join tap_tr_rel_account_info tri2 on tri2.trai_tr_volgnummer = s1.trai_tr_volgnummer and tri2.trai_tr_account_code = 1 left outer join tap_tr_rel_account_info tri3 on tri3.trai_tr_volgnummer = s1.trai_tr_volgnummer and tri3.trai_tr_account_code = decode(tri2.trai_tr_account_code,1,2,2,2,3,4,4,4,7,7,NULL)
